{"tid":2093180,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"將《願榮光歸香港》變成港版rickroll","createTime":"2020-07-03T16:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T07:57:15.000Z","uid":99956,"like":125,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ea7fdce2d96a6480273f318b68a020ffbe487921","tid":2093180,"uid":99956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:07:33.000Z","msg":"國安法實施之後，係街到播呢首歌可能會犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有冇諗過係任何地方 (藍絲fb group, 討論區, 藍絲屋企人群組)<br />\n瘋狂貼香港國歌既link <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後係貼link既同時加返一個適宜既標題，去吸引(呃) d藍絲係街到播？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n*(再加上藍絲廢老好中意係街或者車入面唔帶耳筒睇片)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n*(亦都唔一定就係rickroll 國歌，其他對我地有利既片都可以咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係非標準示範 (因為連登貼link會出埋預覽，但Whatsapp / facebook 等地方可以cut咗個預覽佢，令到藍絲唔會知道條link係飛去邊) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ziiBfb1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FziiBfb1.png&h=45c97def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g&amp;lc=Ugw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoUIDL4SB60g%26lc%3DUgw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=99ce3403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g&amp;lc=Ugw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg</a><br />\n［開聲聽］快速領取政府一萬蚊👆🏻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g&amp;lc=Ugw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoUIDL4SB60g%26lc%3DUgw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=99ce3403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g&amp;lc=Ugw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg</a><br />\nd黃絲真係痴撚線👆🏻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g&amp;lc=Ugw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoUIDL4SB60g%26lc%3DUgw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=99ce3403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g&amp;lc=Ugw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg</a><br />\n支持政府，我愛香港警察👆🏻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g&amp;lc=Ugw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoUIDL4SB60g%26lc%3DUgw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=99ce3403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g&amp;lc=Ugw1EYUSAixCRjDiVs14AaABAg</a><br />\n支持香港國安法👆🏻<br />\n<br />\n希望通過將《願榮光歸香港》變成港版rickroll，令到藍絲瘋狂係街到聽，觸犯國安法就唔係咁好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d16203c66e232ba89fcd752caa1f2f8fc12b40c","tid":2093180,"uid":99956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:09:02.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"7c6da2859d090747239b2d9cf96b4203022cc2e5","tid":2093180,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:09:39.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"c04941564b8c7d2f3675c5b14738aaba20e0c898","tid":2093180,"uid":99956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12277142f58b458110587947e304679ca1cc4e32","tid":2093180,"uid":99956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd30691c08226ee0d7b830259d16cf0526